node.text:
My answer here varies a little but my mentality is steadfast. 

When it’s midnight and all my business is done for the day - and the only thing left on my “to do” list is workout..

Two things I think about 🧠 

• I’ll remind myself of how things used to be many years ago… those fun $7 bucks days. 

• Then in the quiet of the night when no one is watching or listening, I’ll ask one of the most important questions we can ask ourselves in this moment. 

How bad of a motherfucker do you think you are? 

Then I’ll usually start belly laughing like a crazy person while nodding my head and say 
“Fuck you. Let’s fucking GO” 

And off we go 😊

#projectrock 
#midnightoilburners🕯 
#hardestworkersintheroom

node.title: What’s my mental process to push thru fatigue and being tired ⁉️

to life
the journey.. 🥃

node.text:
Thank you @hollywoodcriticsassociation for awarding BEST BROADCAST NETWORK SERIES: COMEDY to our NBC series ~ YOUNG ROCK 🌺💪🏾

This show has always been a very surreal and humbling experience for me considering it’s based off of my wild and true life story - that will always be anchored in life’s greatest blessings ~ gratitude and family. 

THANK YOU guys - the audience - my #1 boss 😊 - for tuning in every week to share in our stories and MANA. 

And finally, a huge CONGRATS TO OUR TALENTED YOUNG ROCK CAST. 
The real ones who brought life, soul, humanity and HUMOR and CULTURE to homes around the world. 

Season 2 here we come!!!

#HCAAwards 
#BestBroadcastNetworkSeries
#Comedy 
#YOUNGROCK 🌺💪🏾🥃

node.title: Grateful to the bone to accept this amazing HCA Award for YOUNG ROCK 🌺💪🏾

node.text:
Anna, 

I was so moved by your story and humbled to hear what a huge fan you are of mine. 

And now, I am YOUR biggest fan. 
Your strength inspires us all. 

+ Plus, I’m certain I’m literally your biggest fan because I’m the size of a dinosaur and I’m as old as one too! 
🤣 🦖 

Stay strong Anna…keep the faith and keep your fight alive!! 

I hope this put a smile on your face and we are sending all the positive energy and mana we got. 

Love, 

DJ and the millions who will see this message 🖤🌎

node.title: Somewhere in Middletown, PA... @apayne226 is SHOCKED by this surprise!! 🥰

node.text:
Hey you guys know where I can find The Rock? 

Sometimes they go bat shit crazy with screams so loud they wake the dead 
🤯💀📢

And sometimes they - literally - become paralyzed and speechless 😶🙊

Either way, this is some of the best parts of fame - making a few folks happy. 
And speechless 😂

#tourbusshenanigans 
#therockshood 🛻

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by therock on September 06, 2021. May be an image of food and indoor.

node.text:
Midnight heaven 🍪🍰🥃

Double chocolate/peanut butter chip 
Oatmeal raisin 
Double chocolate chip 
Chocolate chip walnut 
Insanely delicious coffee cake 

Frost bitten & chilled @teremana 

COUNT ME IN on @netflix. 
Easily one of the best docs I’ve seen in a very long time ~ HIGHLY recommend. 
🥁🪘🎶 
(I would’ve loved to have watched this with my father in law, Sib Hashian. Drummer for one of the greatest rock and roll bands of all time - BOSTON) 

Enjoy your cheat meals, my friends. 

#cheatmealsunday 🥃🥁

node.text:
My answer here varies a little but my mentality is steadfast. 

When it’s midnight and all my business is done for the day - and the only thing left on my “to do” list is workout..

Two things I think about 🧠 

• I’ll remind myself of how things used to be many years ago… those fun $7 bucks days. 

• Then in the quiet of the night when no one is watching or listening, I’ll ask one of the most important questions we can ask ourselves in this moment. 

How bad of a motherfucker do you think you are? 

Then I’ll usually start belly laughing like a crazy person while nodding my head and say 
“Fuck you. Let’s fucking GO” 

And off we go 😊

#projectrock 
#midnightoilburners🕯 
#hardestworkersintheroom

Been one of those long weeks, but we’ve all had em. 

Yes, we only live once ~ but truth is, every time we open our eyes, we live again. 

One more shot, one more chance, one more opportunity to live FULL. 

But, we only die once ~ @yomicoart 

1230am. Saturday night. 
Been a long week… we’ve all been there. 

to life
the journey.. 🥃

node.text:
And of the things that will bite..
‘Til the Sandman, he comes. 
#saturday
#clanginandbangin 
#ironparadiserage 
#hardestworkersinanyroom 

Get after it this weekend, my friends.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by therock on September 04, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, child and indoor.

node.text:
Weekend breakfast vibes ☀️❤️💪🏾

These days Tia loves “hiding” behind daddy. 

But there’s gonna be a time when she gets older where daddy’s arm is the last and un-coolest place she’ll want to be 😌 so I’ll take these moments 24/7. 

Fun irony is she’s hiding behind the part of my tattoo where it tells the story (symbolically) of protection. 

Always protecting my AIGA (family) 🌊🦈 

#breakastvibes 
#daddysarm
#coolestplacetobe 
#tilshebecomesateenager 😎
